  "description": "Trefoil tangle at 0.6 creates stepped harmonic shifts — the knot crossings act like note quantization steps in the FDN routing. 0.9 Hz pulse rate with S&H on filter creates irregular gate patterns. This preset sounds like a sequence playing through a topological filter: pitched, rhythmic, unpredictable.",
